63.5	There_Will_Be_Blood	There Will Be Blood	There Will Be Blood is a 2007 drama film written, co-produced, and directed by Paul Thomas Anderson. The film is loosely based on Upton Sinclair's 1927 novel Oil!. It tells the story of a gold miner-turned-oilman on a ruthless quest for wealth during Southern California's oil boom of the late 19th and early 20th centuries. It stars Daniel Day-Lewis and Paul Dano.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a5/There_will_be_blood.jpg/215px-There_will_be_blood.jpg
